UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='纳拉雷克斯又陷入了沉睡！$B$B很久以前，纳拉雷克斯曾满怀着进入翡翠梦境、让贫瘠之地重新变成茂密森林的伟大理想而来到了这处洞穴中。但他的执着却逐渐消退了，而他的思想也被脑海蜿蜒的幻象所侵染。$B$B现在，那些奇怪的爬虫正从他的梦境中爬到这片土地上来，我们必须把他从梦魇中唤醒过来，否则他就将永远失落于其中，并继续给这片大地带来邪恶的力量！$B$B不过，只有杀死他那些堕落的仆人──毒牙之王，我才能开始进行唤醒仪式。'	-- Naralex sleeps again!$b$bLong ago, Naralex journeyed to this cavern with the honorable goal of entering the Emerald Dream and regrowing the Barrens into a lush forest. His focus waned and his thoughts became tainted by serpentine visions.$b$bNow, reptilian beasts seep from his dreams to the land. He must be awoken from the nightmare or he will be forever lost, and a great evil unleashed.$b$bOnly after his corrupted servants, the Fanglords, have been slain can I perform the awakening ritual.
