UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我知道你是谁，$N。由于某种原因，命运将你带到我面前，而且我对此并不感到高兴。在未来的日子里，你将做出很多抉择，我希望你拥有足够的智慧来做出正确的抉择。$B$B相信我吧，$R，──总有正确的抉择。'	-- I know who you are, $N.  Fate and forces beyond that have brought you to me for a reason, and it is one I take no pleasure in being a part of.  There are many decisions you will make in the coming times, and I hope you are wise enough to make the correct ones.$B$BBelieve me, $r, when I tell you this - there are correct choices.
