UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你来到此地仅仅是第一步……如果你想帮助伊瑟拉的绿龙军团，这是个正确的选择。$B$B你到这儿来也许只是受到个人利益的驱使，也许是受到良心的谴责。什么缘由并不重要，重要的是结果：伊兰尼库斯所经受的痛苦令我从梦中惊醒，现在我要终止他的痛苦。我想请你帮助我完成这项任务。'	-- The fact that you are here is a first step... a correct choice if you will, in aiding Ysera's Dragonflight.$B$BYou may be here for purely the lure of personal gain, or you may be here because you are morally compelled.  Neither reason is important on its own, but both are in fact critical to this end: The agony that Eranikus endures is what rousted me from my Dream, and it is now my charge to see his torment ended.  I now ask you to aid me in this quest.
