UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我那柄巨大的战锤──铁胆之锤，被交给了新的建筑大师弗诺斯·达克维尔。这个家伙人品低劣，才疏学浅。$B$B这点就是你需要知道的，$N。我想阻止他。他无法将铁胆之锤的力量发挥到极致，但是如果他的后续者有这个能力的话，他们就会毁掉一切的，而这必将带来灾难性的后果。'	-- My great hammer, Ironfel, was handed down to the new chief architect, Fineous Darkvire: A man of despicable motive and little talent.$B$BThis is where you come in, $N. I want him stopped. He is too inept to harness the true power of Ironfel, but should one come after him with the aptitude to use Ironfel to its full potential, the destruction they could cause with their creations would be disastrous to this world.
