	`Text_lang`='啊，你必须去雷霆崖最高处拜访他们中的一人。沿着血蹄村北面的道路走。雷霆崖底有升降梯可达顶部。当你到达那儿时，可以询问雷霆崖守卫。'	-- Ah, you must go to the great heights of Thunder Bluff to visit one of those.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village.  At the base of the bluffs is an elevator that will take you to the top.  When you get there ask for further directions from one of the Bluffwatchers.
