UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='在北方的雷霆崖，有一名双足飞龙管理员。乘坐升降梯到达雷霆崖顶部，问问那儿的守卫，他们会为你指明方向的。'	-- There is a Wind Rider Master in the great city of Thunder Bluff to the north.  Ride the elevator from the base of Thunder Bluff to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for further instructions.
WHERE `Id`=6666 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='在北方的雷霆崖，有一名双足飞龙管理员。乘坐升降梯到达雷霆崖顶部，问问那儿的守卫，他们会为你指明方向的。'	-- Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions.
WHERE `Id`=6667 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

