UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='很高兴见到你，$C。除非你和我的女主人玛加萨之间有直接交易关系，否则别找我说话。$B$B我帮她处理大部分的事务，让她能集中精力处理更重要的事情。或许在你拜见她之前我们可以谈谈。'	-- Well met, $c. You may speak to me unless you have direct business with my mistress Magatha.$B$BI deal with most of her tasks for her so she can concentrate on more important matters. Perhaps there are some things we could discuss before you seek audience with her?
