UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='由于我的身份问题，我并未对你说实话，我必须为此向你道歉。我必须确定你是值得信赖的──很少有人能无私地为一个年老的隐士提供帮助。$B$B你已经证明了自己是个正直崇高的人。'	-- I must apologize for not being entirely truthful with you in regards to my identity. I had to be certain that you could be trusted - few people would have selflessly lent assistance to an old and forgotten hermit.$B$BYou have proven yourself as one of those people: A person of integrity and honor.
