	`Text_lang`='欢迎你，我的$G兄弟:姐妹;。如果你想接受训练，我会很乐意教你的。$B$B重申自己在这伟大的平衡中的地位总是无伤大雅的。作为这种平衡的守护者，我们必须努力保持清醒的头脑和坚定的信念。训练能使我们做到这一点。'	-- Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to teach you.$B$BIt never hurts to reaffirm one's place within what I like to call the Great Balance.  As preservers of this balance, we must strive to continually keep our minds clear and our hearts strong.  Training helps us in this regard.
