	`Text_lang`='记住，所有的事物都是有关联的。如果陆地上的野兽灭绝，我们的种族将在孤独中死去，因为牛头人和野兽的命运是相通的，而艾泽拉斯的命运和所有艾泽拉斯上的生灵的命运也休戚相关。'	-- Remember, all things are connected. If the beasts were gone from the land, our kind would die from a great loneliness of spirit, for whatever happens to the beasts also happens to the Tauren. Whatever befalls Azeroth befalls all those that inhabit it.
