UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='不幸的是，对于拥有像你这样经历的人来说我没有什么可教的，我的朋友。找到暗夜精灵希尔瓦娜·林月，她住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。'	-- Unfortunately, there is little I can teach someone with your experience, my friend. Seek out the night elf Sylvanna Forestmoon, who resides in the Craftsmen's Terrace of Darnassus.
