UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='(达纳苏斯语)愿伊露恩与你同在，我的$G兄弟:姐妹;。我们这里欢迎你。'	-- Elune-adore, my $gbrother:sister;. You are welcome here. Speak, and I will do what I can to aid you.
