UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='是我亲爱的恋人卡利派你来找我的？她可是我的宝贝。'	-- Did my sweet lass Kali send you down to me? The apple of my eye, she is.
WHERE `Id`=7692 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我教不了你，$N。去找塔雷·浆泡；她是一个侏儒，住在铁炉堡的侏儒区。哦，既然你反正要去，请把我的爱带给卡利。'	-- Ye're beyond my skill to teach, $N. Go pester Tally Berryfizz; she's a gnome living in Tinker Town of Ironforge. Oh, and since you're headed up anyway, give Kali my love.
WHERE `Id`=7694 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='别被那些天真的大眼睛欺骗了。塔雷是个专家，我每天都在学习新知识。你认为我为什么会在侏儒区？你看我像个工程师吗？啊，我可不这么想。'	-- Don't let those big, innocent eyes fool ye. Tally's an expert, all right: I learn something new every day. Why d'you think I'm here in Tinker Town? Do I look like an engineer to you? Aye, I didn't think so.
WHERE `Id`=7695 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='哦，我无法教你任何东西，$N。跟那边的塔利·浆泡谈谈。她几乎构不着桌子，但是当她在配制药水时，你得小心一点！'	-- Och, there's nothing I can teach ye, $N. Have a word with Tally Berryfizz over there. She can hardly reach the tables, but when she starts brewing a potion, watch out!
WHERE `Id`=7697 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你看起来像是个喜欢冒险的人。而我，自从我们巨魔来到这里我就受够冒险了。现在我每天都是既来之则安之，而且我训练其他家伙替我冒险。'	-- You got the look of someone wantin' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an' I train other folks to handle adventures for me.
WHERE `Id`=7698 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='桌上的所有瓶子中都盛有今天配制好的药水。心急吃不到热豆腐。哈哈！'	-- All the bottles on this table are potions I brewed today. And they say a watched pot never boils. Ha!
WHERE `Id`=7701 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='他们说我愚蠢，我要证明自己的实力。我要关注所有的罐子，证明它们都能煮东西。我的好运就要来了！谁是愚蠢的人，嗯？嗯！？'	-- They called me stupid, but I'll show them. I'm going to watch every pot I have and prove that they can all boil stuff anyway. Yeah, I'm on a roll! Who's stupid now, huh? Huh!?
WHERE `Id`=7702 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='不能帮你。你比我更懂药剂。还有，我还要看着罐子。去找那边的耶尔玛克谈谈。他懂得很多药剂的知识。'	-- Can't help you. You know more about potions than I do. Besides, I have pots to watch. Talk to Yelmak over there. He knows a lot about potions.
WHERE `Id`=7703 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='贝娜就像着魔一样工作。她日以继夜地调制这些药剂，不吃不睡。我知道我们的亡灵盟友需要帮助，但是我担心她这样会伤身体的。'	-- Bena works like one possessed. Day and night I have seen her bent over these potions, often going without sleep or food. I know our undead allies need help, but I begin to fear she will do herself an injury.
WHERE `Id`=7704 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你学习的能力已经超过我了。你需要找那边的贝娜·冰蹄谈谈以获得更多指示。但请不要占用她太多时间。她需要休息。'	-- Your capacity for learning has outstripped mine. You will need to talk to Bena Winterhoof over there for further instruction. Please don't take too much of her time, though. She needs her rest.
WHERE `Id`=7706 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='能看到一张友善的脸真不错。我没有跟药剂师乔汉聊过很多，除非他想要什么东西。他离开坟墓太久了。有一天我也会像他一样，我听说。真可怕。或许到那时我就不在乎了。'	-- Nice to see a friendly face. I don't get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He's been out of the grave too long. Someday I'll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won't care.
WHERE `Id`=7707 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你是来学习配制药水的？我能传授给你很多知识。虽然我已年老力衰，但脑子还是管用的。'	-- Here to learn about potions? I've got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven't lost my brains. Yet.
WHERE `Id`=7708 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我很珍惜我们之间的友谊，但是让我们面对现实吧：你对药水的了解比我多。要是你想得到训练的话，就找亡灵马许医生谈谈。他居住在幽暗城的炼金房。'	-- I appreciate the company, but let's face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He's a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.
WHERE `Id`=7709 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='这是真的，我曾经是人类。缺点是可能转换为我们的优势的，$N，因为我对人类的劣势了若指掌。'	-- Once, it is true, I was human. What might otherwise be a shortcoming works to our advantage, $N, for I know human weaknesses intimately.
WHERE `Id`=7710 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你对药剂的知识已经远胜于我，但你还有很多要学的。上楼去到东南面见见马许医生。他会交给你真正的苦痛──啊咳。他是一个被遗忘者，他能进一步训练你。'	-- Your knowledge of potions has exceeded mine, but you still have much to learn. Go up the stairs to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. He will teach you true sufferi--ahem. He is a Forsaken who will train you further.
WHERE `Id`=7712 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='别那样看我。我也许跟你不同，我不是个冒险家，但是这并不意味着我的力量比你小。忙碌的生活会让你的手臂变得强壮的。'	-- Stop giving me that look. I may not be an adventurer like you, but that doesn't mean I can't have a few muscles. All that stirring makes your arms strong.
WHERE `Id`=7713 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我没有什么可教你的了。但是，我听说有位名叫安尼希尔的暗夜精灵也许能教你。她居住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。'	-- There's nothing more I can teach you. I've heard of a night elf who might be able to, though. Her name is Ainethil, and she lives in the Craftsmen's Terrace of Darnassus.
WHERE `Id`=7714 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你需要我的帮助？可以。你需要什么？'	-- You want my help? You got it. What do you need?
WHERE `Id`=7717 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='别被沃萨亮晶晶的眼睛和浓密的胡须愚弄了。他是个很有才能的学徒，也是个很好的朋友，即使我在跟他谈话时颈部有些痉挛。'	-- Don't let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur's a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him.
WHERE `Id`=7718 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗯，我能教的你已经都学会了。或许你该找其他人谈谈了。试一下达纳苏斯工匠区的暗夜精灵安尼希尔。她确实很有智慧！'	-- Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it's time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen's Terrace of Darnassus. She's got some real talent!
WHERE `Id`=7719 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你是谁？为什么骚扰我？哦，是啦──你是学生吧。是的。我能为你做什么吗？'	-- Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you?
WHERE `Id`=7722 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='(达纳苏斯语)祝你与家人好运，$N。你是来寻求知识的吗？'	-- Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge?
WHERE `Id`=7723 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

-- UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
-- 	`Text_lang`='My apologies, $N, but I do not offer instruction to novices. Instead, talk to Milla Fairancora in the Craftsmen''s Terrace of Darnassus. She can help you make up for lost time.'	-- My apologies, $N, but I do not offer instruction to novices. Instead, talk to Milla Fairancora in the Craftsmen's Terrace of Darnassus. She can help you make up for lost time.
-- WHERE `Id`=7725 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='虽然我很高兴听到你对我的能力充满信心，但我真的没法再教你了。你必须到达纳苏斯的工匠区去找暗夜精灵安尼希尔谈谈。她可以帮助你。'	-- Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen's Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you.
WHERE `Id`=7727 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='即使轻微地改变药剂的成份也能使它发生根本的变化。耐心和精确，年轻人：他们会让你在所有行业都受益匪浅。'	-- Even slight alterations to a potion's ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life.
WHERE `Id`=7728 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我制造药剂的技能在你之下。你应该与那边的安尼希尔谈谈。她会明白你需要进一步的培训。'	-- My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction.
WHERE `Id`=7729 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='啊，又回到年轻的时候了，还有第一次发现药剂的时候。谢谢你恢复我的记忆，$N。去跟那边的米拉·法拉科纳分享那份年轻的热情吧。'	-- Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there.
WHERE `Id`=7731 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我已经用多年学会了很多药剂知识，$N，而那些知识都由你支配。你只需提要求就可以。'	-- I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask.
WHERE `Id`=7732 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我很忙，$N。告诉伍特去处理一切。那个年轻人整天都焦虑不安的。他大部分时间都处于这种状态，像是要做些什么。'	-- I'm busy, $N. Tell Whuut to handle whatever it is. That young pup has been stewing all day long. He spends much more time like that, and he's going to hurt something.
WHERE `Id`=7733 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='见到你是我的荣幸，$N，但是你在配制药水方面比我厉害。去幽暗城 炼金房找亡灵赫伯特·哈尔希医生。他能帮助你。'	-- I'm honored to meet you, $N, but your skill at potions is greater than my own. Go see Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He can help you from now on.
WHERE `Id`=7734 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你找错兽人了。我不训练新手。去问问那边的小伍特……谦虚一点。'	-- You're talking to the wrong orc. I don't train novices. Talk to young Whuut over there... and use small words.
WHERE `Id`=7736 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='另一名学生，是吗？好吧。我看看有什么能帮助你的。'	-- Another student, eh? All right. I'll see what I can do to help you out.
WHERE `Id`=7737 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='格里克斯和我达成一项共识：他给我供货，而我给他钱。这是很认真的！那个海贼为了一小袋皱皱巴巴的皇血草收我多少钱……足够把一个成年的地精弄哭了。'	-- Glyx and I have an understanding: he keeps me supplied, and I keep him rich. Seriously! What that pirate charges me for a measly pouch of crumpled kingsblood... it's enough to make a grown goblin cry.
WHERE `Id`=7738 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你做得比我要好！你需要一个经验比我还要多的人。那就是安尼希尔，一个在达纳苏斯工匠区生活的暗夜精灵女士。'	-- You're better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I've got. That'd be Ainethil, a night elf lady who lives in the Craftsmen's Terrace of Darnassus.
WHERE `Id`=7742 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='第一次看见亡灵时，我哭了，我无法想像他们的恐惧和孤寂。大地之母在我耳边吟唱，她告诉我：「拯救他们吧。」'	-- When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them."
WHERE `Id`=7743 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你制造药剂的技术已经在我之上。去幽暗城的炼金房找亡灵赫伯特·哈尔希医生。他可以继续你的训练，而你也可以亲眼目睹他的人民所遭受的苦难。'	-- Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people's plight.
WHERE `Id`=7747 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='又来打扰我了。像这样我还能做什么工作么？不用回答，我看起来像是很在乎你的回答么？如果我们要清理这个地方并且扩张我们帝国的话，我需要绝对的安静！'	-- Another interruption. How am I supposed to get any work done like this? Don't answer that; do I look as if I care what you have to say? Why don't you go bother Mr. High-And-Mighty instead?
WHERE `Id`=7748 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='要我训练你？别开玩笑了──我们都知道这是不可能的。我可无法胜任。你要是想接受训练的话，就去幽暗城的炼金房找被遗忘者赫伯特·哈尔希医生吧。'	-- Me, train you? Come on--we both know I can't. It's this teaching, you see. My own skills suffer. You want training, go to Doctor Herbert Halsey, a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.
WHERE `Id`=7749 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='有奥格诺恩提供所需的供应，我可以不用寻找一株草药就能完成在这里的任务。如果我永远都不用再次看到自然的奇迹，这就不会很快发生。'	-- With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won't be too soon.
WHERE `Id`=7754 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我没有可传授给你的知识了。穿过拱门走下斜坡到东南方，找赫伯特·哈尔希医生谈谈。他是个被遗忘者，他能教给你更加高级的技术。'	-- I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques.
WHERE `Id`=7755 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='到这儿来学习的吗？很好。我想要是我教你的话，你不会对我们的联盟造成太多的伤害。只要你一心对付我们的敌人。'	-- Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can't cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies.
WHERE `Id`=7758 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='虽然每次我都使用了相同的成分，但配制出的药水似乎都达不到预期的治疗效果。这只能得出一个结论：植物发生了变化。我还不清楚具体原因。'	-- This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what.
WHERE `Id`=7759 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='现在你该找一位更加渊博的老师了。在菲拉斯的羽月要塞居住着暗夜精灵凯兰娜·风语。她有聪明的头脑；毫无疑问她能继续教你。'	-- It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further.
WHERE `Id`=7760 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你制造药剂的技能需要再高超一些才能当我的学生。在此期间，在那边的希尔瓦娜·林月或米拉·法拉科纳可能会帮助你。'	-- Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there.
WHERE `Id`=7762 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你的培训进展很好。你该为你的成就感到自豪。'	-- Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments.
WHERE `Id`=7763 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我和我的同伴正在收集我们所知的致命物质，并在敌人身上测试它们的效果。一旦我收集齐备，我将制造出这世界前所未有的瘟疫。'	-- My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen.
WHERE `Id`=7764 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='难以置信。你配制药水的技能已经能跟我匹敌了。我不能再训练你了，去悲伤沼泽找斯通纳德的兽人罗格瓦尔谈谈。他以他的宝刀而闻名。'	-- Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He's known for his cutting-edge experiments.
WHERE `Id`=7765 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你的技术太差了，还不能跟我学习。去跟那边的马丁医生谈谈，或者爬上斜坡到东南方去看看马许医生。他们是被遗忘者，可以给你所需的训练。'	-- You don't yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need.
WHERE `Id`=7767 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='准备好接受训练了？保持速度，$N。我们要走的路还长着呢。'	-- Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $N. We've got a lot of ground to cover.
WHERE `Id`=7768 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='从前我欢迎过黑暗，因为它是夜晚的姐妹。现在总是漆黑一片，甚至在白天也是这样，而森林迫切需要给养。除非我们快些行动，否则这扩散的荒疫会遍布整个世界。'	-- Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world.
WHERE `Id`=7769 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你是来接受药水配制这一技能的训练的吗？要是你认为能从我这儿不费吹灰之力地学到东西的话，你就大错特错了。走吧，在你没有掌握更高技能之前别来找我。'	-- Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill.
WHERE `Id`=7770 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你的技能显示你一直喜爱我们的艺术，但是我想看到你所做承诺的进一步证据。我会分配给你一项任务。完成它就会令我满意。'	-- Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content.
WHERE `Id`=7771 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='卡拉然，我把火炬弄丢了。给我一个新的吧。'	-- 8479, Kalaran, I have misplaced my torch. I require another.
WHERE `Id`=7773 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='大酋长萨尔亲自邀请我到这儿来。我感到非常荣幸，这并不困难。我不要求自己的职务高于斯通纳德。我只想找些生长在这儿的草药。'	-- Warchief Thrall himself asked me to come out here. I was honored to obey, and it's no hardship. I couldn't have asked for a better posting than Stonard. Just about any herb I might need grows in the muck here.
WHERE `Id`=7774 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗯，好吧，我看到你还懂一点做药剂的方法。然而，你是否配做我的学生仍有待察看。我有一项任务交给你。争取给我一个好印象。'	-- Hmm, well, I can see that you have a little skill at making potions. Whether you're worthy to be my student remains to be seen, however. I have a job for you. Impress me.
WHERE `Id`=7776 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='谢谢你！谢谢你，$G牧师:女祭司;。有了月神的庇护，我就可以对抗那些堕落的树精了！'	-- Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those corrupt timberlings with Elune's power behind me!
WHERE `Id`=7780 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='再见，愿月神与你同在。'	-- Farewell to you, and may Elune be with you always.
WHERE `Id`=7781 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='谢谢！谢谢你，$G祭司:女祭司;。有了你的力量我就可以继续作战了！'	-- Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those humans with your power to back me!
WHERE `Id`=7784 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='再见了，愿我们的祖先永远保佑你！'	-- Farewell to you, and may our ancestors be with you always!
WHERE `Id`=7785 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='谢谢你！谢谢你，牧师。有了你的帮助，我就能对付这些雪怪了！'	-- Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those wendigo with the Light on my side!
WHERE `Id`=7788 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='再见，愿光明与你同在。'	-- Farewell to you, and may the Light be with you always.
WHERE `Id`=7789 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='谢谢你！谢谢你，牧师。有了你的帮助，我就能对付这些豺狼人了！'	-- Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those gnolls with your power to back me!
WHERE `Id`=7792 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='再见，愿暗影永远保护你！'	-- Farewell to you, and may shadow always protect you!
WHERE `Id`=7793 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='只需做些小调整……我们出发吧！'	-- Just a minor adjustment here... ah there we go!
WHERE `Id`=7794 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='%s进入了狂乱状态！'	-- %s goes into a killing frenzy!
WHERE `Id`=7797 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

