UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗯，你学习速度蛮快的！我没办法教你更多知识了，但是宾斯匹德可以！你可以在铁炉堡里找到他。祝你好运！'	-- Well, you're just zooming right along! I can't teach you anything you don't already know, but Springspindle Fizzlegear sure can! You can find Springspindle in Ironforge. Good luck!
