UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='在黑海岸的北面流淌着壁泉河，发源于现今的费伍德森林。随着河流流出并汇入薄雾海，一直蜿蜒到海洋北部最深处。一处被人们称为石爪的地方有你要找的东西。$B$B要当心──蛇颈龙聚集在石爪那里，会攻击侵入他们领地的人。'	-- In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist's Edge, travel north to where the deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due to its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory.
WHERE `Id`=8039 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='草地柔软青葱。空气清新，阳光明媚，歌声飘飘。泰达希尔的梦想终成现实。但是为什么我感到有种不详的预兆？'	-- The grass is soft and lush. The air is fresh, full of light and song. Everything I've seen suggests that Teldrassil is a dream come true. Why, then, is my heart full of foreboding?
WHERE `Id`=8041 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='$G尊敬的先生:女士;，在你掌握制皮的更多知识之前，我还不能帮助你，对此我感到很遗憾。跟法多恩或达丽亚娜谈谈。他们能教你所需的技能。'	-- I regret to say that I cannot aid you, $gnoble sir:gentle lady;, until you learn more of working with leather. Speak with Faldron or Darianna here instead. They can teach you the skill you require.
WHERE `Id`=8044 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='别试图将你的意愿强加到皮革上。而是让其天然的特性显示出自身的形状和功能。这不是一场战役。与皮革协同工作，而不是与其作对。'	-- Do not try to force your will upon the leather. Rather, let its natural tendencies dictate what form and function it will take. This is not a battle to be won. Work with the leather, not against it.
WHERE `Id`=8045 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='针太细，线太粗，针脚倒还不错。我们与萨尔和其他人的合约将继续有效。部落不会被驱逐出这片土地的。'	-- The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands.
WHERE `Id`=8046 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我的才能有限，你也已经达到了。恭喜你，$N。你的下一站应该是菲拉斯的莫沙彻营地。牛头人哈拉纳·铁皮住在那里；她的技术很有声望。'	-- Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill.
WHERE `Id`=8047 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我自己不久前也是一个新手，所以我觉得我不太适合教你。试着跟那边的塔恩或是玛克谈谈。他们之中应该有人能回答你的问题。'	-- It's been so long since I was a novice myself that I don't think I'd be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions.
WHERE `Id`=8049 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='凯恩把我们带到了一片充满希望的大地。我们很幸运，因此我们再把好运带给别人。这就是我为什么开始教学的原因，$N。'	-- Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N.
WHERE `Id`=8050 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我可以利用在这儿找到的材料制作有趣的东西。这些山林中有许多奇怪的生物！去杀死它们，$N。'	-- I can make amazing things with the materials I find out here. By Muradin's beard, there are fantastic creatures in these hills! Go have a whack at them, $N, and bring me back some tall tales.
WHERE `Id`=8051 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我所有的作品都必须由买主亲自来订购。奥尔文常常要我改变这个习惯，但是我就是不改。看看你周围吧，无数战士还指望我给他们打造装甲呢。'	-- All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor.
WHERE `Id`=8055 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我不会在这场战争中让步。我不分昼夜的制造新装甲，还把旧的装甲修补好。我没时间做其他任务。你愿帮我分担一些吗？'	-- We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me?
WHERE `Id`=8057 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你来找我求学是浪费了你我的时间，$N。我没时间教授基础技能。我们在这里战斗，而这里是一处前线。在你准备充分之前不要再来找我。'	-- You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We're fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don't return to me until you are more prepared.
WHERE `Id`=8058 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我觉得你的服饰急需维修。'	-- I can tell that your wardrobe is in dire need of care.
WHERE `Id`=8059 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='生活就像一幅小心编织的锦缎。'	-- Life is like a carefully woven tapestry.
WHERE `Id`=8062 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗯……你需要学的东西有点超出我的能耐了。去找那边的塞拉多斯谈谈。我会的东西全是他教的！'	-- Hmm... the things you need to learn are a little above my head. Have a talk with Sellandus over at Larson's Clothiers just up the path to the right. He taught me everything I know!
WHERE `Id`=8063 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='缝纫需要娴熟的手法，以及……也是最重要的，耐性。'	-- Needlework requires a steady hand. And patience... above all, patience.
WHERE `Id`=8065 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='欢迎来到我的商店。我能为你做什么？'	-- Welcome to me shop. What can I do for ye'?
WHERE `Id`=8068 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='等一下，我只是一个助手。如果你想学那些花哨的东西，找那边的老约莫德·石眉谈谈。'	-- Hold on there, I'm just an assistant. If ye want to start learnin' the fancy stuff, talk to old Stonebrew over there.
WHERE `Id`=8069 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='很好！我一直希望收个新学生。那么就让我们立刻开始吧！'	-- Excellent! I've been hopin' for a new student. Well, let's get started right away then!
WHERE `Id`=8070 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我们使用动物皮毛制作物品。'	-- We use many animal pelts and skins in our creations.
WHERE `Id`=8071 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我知道一些，但我不是专家。祝你好远，玛加尔也是。他就站在商店后面。看看他是否能帮助你，但是小心别惹恼他。他脾气有些暴躁。'	-- I know a few things, but I'm no expert. Lucky for you, Magar is. He's standing near the back of the shop. See if he can help you, but be careful not to rile him. He can be irritable.
WHERE `Id`=8072 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我们没有浪费狩猎而得的动物的任何一部分。'	-- No part of the animals we hunt is wasted.
WHERE `Id`=8074 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='去结交朋友吧。我能帮你吗？'	-- Pleased to make you acquaintance. May I help you?
WHERE `Id`=8077 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我知识渊博，但我还不是专家。你知道你该去找谁谈话吗？雷安诺！她就在不远的地方。到幽暗城打听她的下落。'	-- I am knowledgable, but I am not an expert. You know who you should talk to? Rhiannon! She's not far. Ask around for her in Undercity
WHERE `Id`=8078 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='这么说……你想当一名裁缝？很好，让我们看看你是否具有这样的潜质。'	-- So... you want to be a tailor? Very well, we'll see if you have what it takes.
WHERE `Id`=8079 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='到我们这儿来的客人可不多。你对我感兴趣？'	-- We don't get many visitors out here. May I interest you in something?
WHERE `Id`=8080 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我只是个学生。雷安诺才是专家。她站在那边的木箱旁。你可以从她那儿学到很多东西。'	-- I'm just a student myself, really. Rhiannon's the expert. She's standing by the crates over there. You can learn a lot from her.
WHERE `Id`=8081 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='是的，我认为你有潜力。或许我可以给你看看一两样东西？'	-- Yes, I think you have potential. Maybe I can show you a thing or two.
WHERE `Id`=8082 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='没有比编织更好的宁神方法了。'	-- There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave.
WHERE `Id`=8083 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你的教育正在继续，而你的知识已超越了我。如果你还想继续学习你就必须找玫琳恩谈谈。她会指引你的。'	-- My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me'lynn. She will guide you.
WHERE `Id`=8084 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗨，我能为你做什么呢？'	-- Hey mon, what can I be doin' for you?
WHERE `Id`=8086 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='恐怕我已不再是个文雅谦逊的人了。年龄和无数战争让我的皮肤和灵魂变得坚硬无比。或许这就是凯恩派我来烈日石居的原因……和煦的暖风和温暖的阳光无法减轻我的痛苦。'	-- 11860, I am afraid that I am no longer gentle or humble. Age and countless battles have hardened my skin and soul. Perhaps that is why Cairne assigned me to Sun Rock Retreat... the gentle winds and warm sun does ease the pain.
WHERE `Id`=8089 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我知道你会来的，$N。很高兴再次见到你，朋友。'	-- I knew you would come, $N. It is good to see you again, friend.
WHERE `Id`=8090 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗷！'	-- Yawww!
WHERE `Id`=8091 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你好。我们的蝙蝠训练很严而且吃得不错。你不会找到比他们还快的了。'	-- Greetings.  Our bats are well trained and fed.  You'll not find faster.
WHERE `Id`=8094 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我要如何效劳？'	-- How may I be of service?
WHERE `Id`=8095 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你好，欢迎。我不太擅长微笑，但是相信我；我很高兴能为您服务。'	-- Greetings, and welcome.  I am not very good at smiling, but trust me; I am happy to serve you.
WHERE `Id`=8096 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='角鹰兽是一种高贵而迅捷的动物。这些训练有素的飞兽可以让它们的骑手以很快的速度旅行。'	-- The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance.
WHERE `Id`=8098 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='为了与大陆保持联系，我们会定期派出角鹰兽在鲁瑟兰村和黑海岸之间传递资讯的。'	-- To maintain our link to the mainland, we have hippogryphs constantly flying between Rut'theran Village and Darkshore.
WHERE `Id`=8099 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='泰达希尔海岸边的鱼儿又大又精神。有传言说那是因为我们新的世界之树的快速增长而引起的。'	-- The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause.
WHERE `Id`=8100 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='尽管黑海岸比泰达希尔更危险，但是很多渔夫都在此谋生。'	-- Although the coast of Darkshore is more dangerous than that of Teldrassil, many fishers find profit here.
WHERE `Id`=8101 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='为冒险家服务是我的荣幸，因为他们即将成为英雄。'	-- It is my honor to provide for adventurers, for they are heroes in the making.
WHERE `Id`=8102 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='鹰巢山这边最快的狮鹫兽了。想乘坐吗？'	-- Fastest gryphons this side of Aerie Peak. Want to take a ride?
WHERE `Id`=8104 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='当然！让我们去兜风吧。'	-- 2859, Sure! Let's go for a ride.
WHERE `Id`=8105 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你可以在北部码头搭船前往鲁瑟兰村和达纳苏斯。你可以在南部码头发现穿越无尽之海通往暴风港。西边的码头，直走到底，则航向蓝谜岛，艾克索达的附近。祝你一路平安！'	-- On the northern dock, you can board a ship that will carry you to Rut'theran Village and Darnassus.  From the southern dock, you can find passage across the Great Sea to Menethil Harbor on Khaz Modan.  Safe journeys to you!
WHERE `Id`=8106 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='朋友，保持警惕。除非打一架，否则母龙是不会放弃的。'	-- On guard, friend. The lady dragon will not give in without a fight.
WHERE `Id`=8107 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='这个码头？你可以乘船前往暗夜精灵的领地。地名？嗯，我想是奥伯丁。我不太确定，我只是一名搬运工。'	-- 12657, This dock here?  Well you can catch the ship that goes to that Night Elf place.  What's it's name?  Uhh Auberdine I think.  I don't really know for sure, I just load and unload stuff.
WHERE `Id`=8108 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='就像很久以前在卡拉赞注定的那样，怪物。我来了，带着公正的裁决而来！'	-- As was fated a lifetime ago in Karazhan, monster - I come - and with me I bring justice.
WHERE `Id`=8109 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我的双足飞龙可以在贫瘠之地高速飞翔。'	-- My wind riders are trained to fly quickly through the hot Barrens air.
WHERE `Id`=8111 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='贫瘠之地阳光灼热，那儿的居住者充满敌意，是考验你的力量和决心的最佳地点。'	-- The Barrens, with its hot sun and hostile denizens, is the perfect place to test your strength and fortitude.
WHERE `Id`=8112 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='要将这些桶运送到挖掘点非常困难，但是要获得火药，还得靠我们自己。$B$B我们必须竭尽所能地对抗黑铁！'	-- Delivering these barrels to the excavation site is hard work, but there are so many depending on us to get the blast powder there.$B$BWe must do what we can against the Dark Irons!
WHERE `Id`=8113 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你好。如果你是来找皮件的，那么你会看到我的货品做工精细。'	-- Greetings.  If you are here for leather goods, then you will find my wares well crafted.
WHERE `Id`=8114 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='当坐在一头双足飞龙背上时，你就会发现它的力量和速度的确不是徒有虚名。'	-- When mounted on the back of a wind rider, one sees that its reputation for strength and speed is well earned.
WHERE `Id`=8116 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你操纵得比我要好！你需要一个经验比我还要多的人。那就是赫伯特·哈尔希医生，一个在幽暗城炼金房工作的亡灵。'	-- You're better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I've got. That'd be Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead who works in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.
WHERE `Id`=8117 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='抓住他！抓住这个卑鄙的罪犯和他的同伙！'	-- Seize him! Seize the worthless criminal and his allies!
WHERE `Id`=8119 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='看看我的肉，朋友。你不会想双手空空就进入贫瘠之地吧。'	-- Have a look at my meats, friend.  You won't want to go out into the Barrens without a good stock of provisions.
WHERE `Id`=8120 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='雷吉纳德，你知道，我是不能让你通过的。'	-- Reginald, you know that I cannot let you pass.
WHERE `Id`=8121 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='在你从双足飞龙背上往下俯瞰这个世界之前，不能说你真正活过。'	-- You haven't lived until you've looked down on the world from the back of a wind rider.
WHERE `Id`=8122 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你一定要做你认为是正确的事情，马库斯。我们一起在图拉扬将军麾下服役。他使我们两个成为了今天的样子。他看错我了么？你真的相信我的目的是要破坏我们的联盟吗？我让我们的英雄们蒙羞了吗？'	-- You must do what you think is right, Marcus. We served together under Turalyon. He made us both the men that we are today. Did he err with me? Do you truly believe my intent is to cause harm to our alliance? Would I shame our heroes?
WHERE `Id`=8123 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='%s似乎陷入了沉思。'	-- %s appears lost in contemplation.
WHERE `Id`=8124 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我很惭愧，老朋友。我不知道我该怎么办了。并不是你使那些伟大的英雄蒙羞，而是我。是我和其余堕落的政客们。他们让我们的生命中充满空洞的诺言和无尽的谎言。'	-- I am ashamed, old friend. I know not what I do anymore. It is not you that would dare bring shame to the heroes of legend - it is I. It is I and the rest of these corrupt politicians. They fill our lives with empty promises, unending lies.
WHERE `Id`=8125 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='亲爱的朋友，你警惕的目光让英雄们以你为荣，你对联盟忠心耿耿。你会在必要的时候像那些俯瞰着你的英雄一样，为你的人民做出伟大的牺牲，我对此毫不怀疑。'	-- Dear friend, you honor them with your vigilant watch. You are steadfast in your allegiance. I do not doubt for a moment that you would not give as great a sacrifice for your people as any of the heroes you stand under.
WHERE `Id`=8126 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='退后！你们没看到英雄正在与我们同行吗？'	-- Stand down! Can you not see that heroes walk among us?
WHERE `Id`=8127 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='让开！让他们过去！'	-- Move aside! Let them pass!
WHERE `Id`=8128 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='雷吉纳德·温德索尔不得受到任何伤害！让他安全地通过这里！'	-- Reginald Windsor is not to be harmed! He shall pass through untouched!
WHERE `Id`=8129 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='去吧，雷吉纳德。愿光明指引着你。'	-- Go, Reginald. May the light guide your hand.
WHERE `Id`=8130 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你可以从这个码头找到去塞拉摩的路。记住我的话，那些地方对从联盟去的人们是非常不安全的。一定要小心谨慎。'	-- You can find passage to Theramore from this dock.  Heed my words, those lands are rarely safe to travel for people of the Alliance.  Watch your step and your back.
WHERE `Id`=8131 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我们令祖先蒙羞。我们令牺牲的同胞蒙羞……原谅我吧，雷吉纳德。'	-- We shame our ancestors. We shame those lost to us... forgive me, Reginald.
WHERE `Id`=8132 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='把我挡在这里可不是明智的决定，马库斯。'	-- Holding me here is not the right decision, Marcus.
WHERE `Id`=8133 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='现在是结束她统治的时候了，马库斯。让开，我的朋友。'	-- Now, it is time to bring her reign to an end, Marcus. Stand down, friend.
WHERE `Id`=8134 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你好。'	-- Good day to you.
WHERE `Id`=8136 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='啊，这件达纳苏斯织品品质最好！'	-- Ah, this Darnassian fabric is the finest!
WHERE `Id`=8141 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='嗯，你这个聪明的家伙！我可以明确地告诉你，你知道的比我多！你可别为此自负，如果你想继续学习的话，就去暴风城找乔吉奥·波利罗谈谈吧。听说他是个很好的裁缝！'	-- Well, aren't you the smarty-pants? Ye know more than I do, I can tell ye that! Don't go getting' a big head, but if ye want to keep learnin', have a chat with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. They say he knows his tailorin'!
