	`Text_lang`='通灵学院这个学习亡灵术的学校位于西瘟疫之地的凯尔达隆那个废弃的小岛上。'	-- The School for Necromancy known as Scholomance is on the ruined island of Caer Darrow in the Western Plaguelands.
