UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我默不作声地忽略了对方的侮辱，希望敌国的统治者能够意识到他的失态。当我回来之后，我会把敌国统治者对我的侮辱告知王上。'	-- I not-so-quietly ignore the insult, hoping to instill a fear in the ruler that he may have gaffed.  I then inform my liege of the insult when I return.
WHERE `Id`=10080 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我默默地忽略了这一侮辱。我不会告诉王上，因为我会为了和平而不惜一切代价。这只是一种侮辱──而不是宣战。'	-- I quietly ignore the insult.  I will not tell my liege, as I am to secure peace at all costs.  It's only an insult - not a declaration of war.
WHERE `Id`=10081 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='你的下一个选择在等着你。$B$B你的兄弟想要加入你所在的享有盛名的军队。虽然你对他的热情和忠诚毫不怀疑，但是你担心他的能力还不足以执行军队艰巨的任务。当你无法肯定定他能否应对挑战──这可能会让你和其他人陷入危机──而你的意见将决定他的去留。$B$B做个选择吧。'	-- Your next choice awaits.$B$BYour brother seeks to join the ranks of the prestigious military order you are already a part of.  While you are sure of his commitment and loyalty, his talent and ability to perform the arduous tasks of the order is what you question.  While you are not certain he will be able to rise to the challenge of the order - putting you and others in danger - you are certain that your word alone would allow him in or keep him out.$B$BMake your choice.
