UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我怕你在奥特兰克山谷活不了多久，$C。等你强壮点再回到我们这儿来吧。'	-- I'm afraid ye would not survive long in Alterac Valley, $c.  Come back and see us when you have a few more seasons under your belt.
