UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='$N，现在，奥特兰克山谷的雷矛卫兵需要你助战，共同打败霜狼氏族。这是个获得荣誉、提升声望的大好机会！你需要知道战场军官在哪里，好让他们送你一程吗？'	-- $N, the Stormpike Guard is in need of your aid in the battle against the Frostwolf Clan in Alterac Valley, now more than ever.  The opportunities for honor and repute are greater than ever as well! Will you join the battle?
