UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='我是驻扎在阿拉希盆地的污染者物资供应商卢瑟弗·图恩。随着你在污染者的声望的提升，我可以出售给你一些非常有用的物品。如果你需要修理装备，我也乐意为你服务。'	-- I am Rutherford Twing, the main supplier for the Defilers posted here at Arathi Basin.  As you improve your standing with us, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you might find useful.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services.
