	`Text_lang`='你好，弗兰卡。我听说你可能有一些纳塔莉亚·玛尔利斯的下落的信息。'	-- 15171, Hello, Frankal. I've heard that you might have some information as to the whereabouts of Mistress Natalia Mar'alith.
