UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='哦，就是这样了……先找个椅子，$G小伙子:小姑娘;。$B$B我肯定鲁特加尔已经告诉你一些事情了，因此我将省略一些细节，让你直奔主题。'	-- Oh brother, not this again... Have a seat $g sonny:missy;.$B$BI'm sure Rutgar has told you some of this story already so I'll spare you the boring details and get right down to the nitty gritty.
