UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='欢迎！上前来，不要害羞。这是我最自豪的发明……冲击者5000型超级大炮！她难道不漂亮吗？她实在就是很漂亮啊！看起来对于炮管的中段来说，你的体型稍微大了一点，但是我想这不是什么大问题。飞行充满了乐趣，你想要学学吗？'	-- Welcome! Step right up, don't be shy. This here is my pride and joy... the Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon! Ain't she pretty? You look a little big around the mid section, but I think you'll fit. Flying is so much fun, want to learn how?
