UPDATE `broadcast_text_locale` SET
	`Text_lang`='没什么好说的。达拉然几乎全被阿克蒙德破坏，法杖遗失了，可能遭到故障防护装置机所粉碎了。$B$B有些人相信就是因为法杖，所以引起阿克蒙德的报复。'	-- There is not much more to tell. Dalaran was nearly wholly destroyed by Archimonde, the staff lost, presumably shattered by the barrier's fail-safe mechanisms.$B$BThere are those that believe the staff to be the cause of Archimonde's reprisal.
WHERE `Id`=12036 AND `Locale`='zhCN';

